<A>__{on march 6th 2007 scooter libby was found guilty of perjury, obstruction of justice and making false statements to the fbi, concerning the leaking of valerie plame's identity. he was handed the maximum sentence: two and a half years in prison, and a $250,000 fine. on july 2nd 2007. the president used his executive authority to commute the court's sentence. joe and valerie left washington and found a new home in santa fe. they live there today, with their children.}
